  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/d06b541e185b4a5585ca3ecd6e5f13bb.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>Robin老师带你聊旅行中的英文<br />\n\t</strong>时间：10月21日（星期一）16:00 - 17:00<br />\n\t主讲老师：罗宾（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/21958373/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a>）<br />\n\t公开课地点：O+口语大厅（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>网校名师简介：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong><span>Robin老师</span></strong></span><br />\n\t<span>一个地地道道的英国大粉丝，说英音，看英剧，喝红茶，喜欢格子衬衫，听英伦摇滚。。。对英国的热爱造就了对英语的热爱。希望也能带你们欢喜的走入英语的殿堂~~</span><br />\n\t<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/21958373/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>课堂内容提要：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>1.What do you like to do on vacation?</strong><br />\n\t-Take an exciting trip<br />\n\t-visit a foreign country<br />\n\t-travel through my own country</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2.Discover something new</strong><br />\n\t-Take languages or cooking lessons<br />\n\t-Visit museums and art galleries</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3.Stay home</strong><br />\n\t-Reading<br />\n\t-Do some housework</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>4.Enjoy nature</strong><br />\n\t-Go camping,hiking,or fishing<br />\n\t-Relax at the beach</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>5.Topic</strong><br />\n\tWhich activities do you like to do on vacation?<br />\n\tWhich activities did you do on your last vacation?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>6.Travel advice</strong><br />\n\tYou should tell the driver where you're going before you get on. And you have to have exact change for the fare.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" target=\"_blank